{"tid":1460391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬，我地喬裝割唔割","createTime":"2019-08-13T02:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T03:04:29.000Z","uid":236473,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"21cb41b035c299b6f4811202df4c6582f316ab78","tid":1460391,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:43:44.000Z","msg":"還掂前線宜家叫做有d時間抖下，咁就要好好諗下對策。<br />\n<br />\n琴日克驚認左佢地有喬裝「不同人士」，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">姐係俾曬暗示我地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得主要係前線喬裝就ok。而喬裝唔需要full gear，你睇下d popo 著件黑色背心上面印popo就自稱克驚。咁醒既大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喬裝主要效用係減低傷亡同埋混餚對方。夠勇既可以直情趁混亂融入對方，到時人夠多，想點都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申就到孟蘭節，中國既halloween節日 cosplay下促進中西文化融合only<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f963ee2ffadc8c87ac0462f5960c606ff68132e","tid":1460391,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:43:56.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e3d85a9149ec0748f489a8051cdd38d2dcf615a7","tid":1460391,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"26700479bcb92898a3c40987c848be5e7709d58b","tid":1460391,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:18.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"8faf2bd95de8c7f2247450fd6f9bb153c2290e0d","tid":1460391,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:29.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d4cce93a97df8be68064ef24c1a6359005929f3a","tid":1460391,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"b9cf5a8e5e68da4a21a8a27faf3fcace878a5b72","tid":1460391,"uid":37396,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"喬裝林鄭都唔割"},{"